{"tid":851783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[搶錢!搶糧!搶娘們!] 張建宗：未來10年基建總投資將超過1萬億元","createTime":"2018-10-07T11:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T13:28:30.000Z","uid":149494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2380197581a9d9bc6a1dc98a7331973a7d31a39c","tid":851783,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗在網誌表示，粵港澳三地政府正積極為港珠澳大橋開通作準備，並於上星期一連三日進行聯合試運。香港政府除了派出超過300名政府人員參與試運外，亦邀請了經營跨境運輸業務的相關營辦商參與。他表示，試運取得預期效果，三地政府正總結經驗，向開通的目標進發。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，投資基建等於投資未來。他表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">預計未來5年，香港每年的整體建造工程量會維持在2500億元至3000億元的高水平</span>，當中包括多項工作，除了三跑道系統之外，還有房屋發展、中九龍幹線及龐大的醫院發展計劃等，未來10年，政府在基建的總投資將超過1萬億元。<br />\n<br />\n他又回顧<span style=\"color: red;\">過往10年，政府在基建的投資由每年2百多億元，升至現時的8百多億元</span>。2018/19年度政府總開支預計為5579億港元，其中約856億港元，即15.34%投放在基建工程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8610%E5%B9%B4%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%B8%BD%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%B0%87%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E1%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-013853157.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%258610%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%2581%258E1%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583-013853157.html&d=iJzOaPEr0DzsvL2eetxwT54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1125603c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8610%E5%B9%B4%E5%9F%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%B8%BD%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%B0%87%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E1%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-013853157.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搶呀！兄弟們！搶錢！搶糧！搶娘們！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e65a0924b7e3a30a4418ce5492c2f3fa71dab241","tid":851783,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/e/eb/Img1643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2Fe%2Feb%2FImg1643.jpg&h=6e82128f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64e2acd97e49cd7d58601cbddaaacf6654148d70","tid":851783,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88b70a930f416179d891640fcf22b9838b86cdc","tid":851783,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"成日講經濟效益 但香港市民就係最無得益 仲要係政府比錢大陸班人黎香港炒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e34564395f8eaf675cc75c78a81b8028d66bac0","tid":851783,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c88b70a930f416179d891640fcf22b9838b86cdc","tid":851783,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"成日講經濟效益 但香港市民就係最無得益 仲要係政府比錢大陸班人黎香港炒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"政府在基建的投資由每年2百多億元，升至現時的8百多億元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留意每單基建有咩國家既公司參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}